</strong></h3><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-iLLNPL gTJAOY pf-79_ pf-heading-1-h3">Routine is essential for many autistic individuals. Changes in sleep patterns or bedtime routines can lead to significant disruptions. Consistency helps to reinforce the body’s natural sleep-wake cycle.
